50|$|Douglas Carl (August 12, 1951 - August 17, 1997) was a {{state senator}} in Michigan who also ran as the Republican nominee in Michigan's 12th Congressional District in 1988 and in the 10th Congressional District in 1992, losing to <b>David</b> <b>Bonior</b> both times.|$|E
